{"type": "article", "id": 5539, "title": "无线音响 Tube Audio", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-26T07:19:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233958XYfaU1cL8dVHrE2M.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自荷兰的设计品牌 LEFF Amsterdam 日前邀请本土设计师 Piet Hein Eek 带来了一款无线音响的作品 Tube Audio。Piet Hein Eek 在造型上沿用了之前发布的 Tube Clock 的精巧轮廓，小圆筒状与金、银、铜 3 种配色的组合颇显质感。Tube Audio 内置了高水准的音效配件，支持 USB 充电和 7 米范围内的蓝牙连接操控，续航时间达 8 小时。定价 149 欧元（约合人民币 1040 元），<a href=\"http://leffamsterdam.com/product-category/tube-audio/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233957qTfmFpiVSMWyABdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233957TrMERCB36atWh8fi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233957df4z6hymIiUMLkBA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}